# NAMA COFFEE Design

**Baca `DESIGN.md` di root project sebelum mengubah layout, warna, hero, navbar, atau gambar.**

## Quick Reference

- **Theme:** Dark premium — bg `#0A0A0A`, teks `#F5F2ED`, aksen `#6F4E37`
- **Hero:** `bg.png` via CSS (`auto 100%` + `right bottom`), gradient kiri, jangan overlay cup terpisah
- **Navbar:** Fixed, blur di layer terpisah (`backdrop-blur-md` + `translateZ(0)`), logo NA/MA, menu uppercase
- **Section title:** `font-black` besar + underline `w-20 h-1.5 bg-[#6F4E37]`
- **CTA:** Rounded-full, ivory primary / outline secondary
- **Gambar tempat:** `PlaceImage` + `tempat1–4.png` di `public/images/`
- **Data bisnis:** `lib/constants.ts` — jangan hardcode phone/IG/maps

## Jangan

- View Transitions / intercept link click
- `transition-all` (pakai `transition-colors`)
- `bg-cover center` untuk hero background
- Improvise warna/font di luar palette

## Inner pages

Menu & Kontak pakai dark theme penuh (sama landing).
